  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, TM are applied in bioinformatics for gene sequence classification or gene expression profiling.",
    "Whilst in domains such as technology, TM techniques are deployed for aspect extraction or to identify user preferences in order to enhance NLP applications such as sentiment analysis, recommendation system, question and answering system.",
    "These applications are discussed in detail in this paper proposes the conceptual framework to provide stakeholders, practitioners and researchers a better understanding of TM applications and helps provide a summary of current knowledge on TM applications.",
    "This study aimed to provide a comprehensive overview of TM, specific to bibliometric analysis and TM applications.",
    "We adopted a high volume of publications (16,941 documents), over 2 decades (2004) (2005) (2006) (2007) (2008) (2009) (2010) (2011) (2012) (2013) (2014) (2015) (2016) (2017) (2018) (2019) (2020) (2021) (2022) (2023)."
  ]
}